I ran into this same problem and had to make an additional change apart from the one mentioned by @momeara to get it to build:
In the file   tensorflow/stream_executor/cuda/cuda_dnn.cc
Change:
#include "cuda/include/cudnn.h"
into:
#include "cuda/cudnn.h"

